DataLayer.Source: SELECT pkey, Fld_Field_1 AS 'Propery ID',Fld_Field_4 AS 'Description',FLD_FIELD_5 AS 'Type Description',FLD_STATE AS State FROM V_XL_TBL_SECTION_10

SqlQuery.Source:
SELECT P.pkey AS 'PKEY', PMKEY.PROPKEY AS 'FKEY_PARENT', IFNULL(Fld_Field_4,'') AS 'Lease Number', IFNULL(Fld_Field_33,'') AS 'Tenant Number',IFNULL(Fld_Field_32,'') AS 'Tenant Name', IFNULL(Fld_Field_34,'') AS 'DBA Name',LT.Commencement,LT.`Expiration Date` FROM V_XL_TBL_SECTION_1 P INNER JOIN (SELECT pkey, Fld_Field_21 AS 'PropKey' FROM TBL_SECTION_1) PMKEY ON PMKEY.pkey = P.pkey INNER JOIN (SELECT FKEY_PARENT AS 'FKEY_PARENT',IFNULL(CONVERT(DATE_FORMAT(MIN(STR_TO_DATE(Fld_Field_3,'%m/%d/%Y')),'%m/%d/%Y') USING utf8),'') AS 'Commencement',IFNULL(CONVERT(DATE_FORMAT(MAX(STR_TO_DATE(Fld_Field_12,'%m/%d/%Y')),'%m/%d/%Y') USING utf8),'') AS 'Expiration Date' FROM V_XL_TBL_SECTION_14
WHERE Fld_Field_3 IS NOT NULL AND Fld_Field_12 IS NOT NULL GROUP BY FKEY_PARENT) LT ON P.PKEY = LT.FKEY_PARENT WHERE IFNULL(P.Fld_FKey_Field_36,'') <> ''
